title: San Juan Island National Historical Park: News
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     News             News         Re-enactors prepare food in the 19th century field kitchen during an annual Encampment at English Camp. The event, scheduled July 26-27, 2014, is widely promoted throughout the Pacific Northwest. NPS Photo  Whether it be a press release announcing a new program or our annual Guide to English and American Camps, park staff and volunteers are committed to keeping the public informed.
